<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../../partials/head') %>
<body class="bg-[#0F172A] text-slate-200 min-h-screen flex font-sans">
    
    <%- include('../../partials/sidebar') %>

    <main class="ml-0 md:ml-64 flex-1 p-6 md:p-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto transition-all duration-300 w-full">
        
        <div class="md:hidden flex items-center justify-between mb-8 pb-4 border-b border-slate-800">
            <button onclick="window.toggleSidebar()" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white focus:outline-none p-1">
                <i class="ri-menu-line text-2xl"></i>
            </button>
            <span class="text-xl font-bold italic text-blue-500 tracking-wider">IDEATE</span>
            <div class="w-8"></div> </div>

        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 md:mb-10 text-sm md:text-base">Got questions? We've got answers.</p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
            <details class="bg-slate-900 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 group open:border-blue-500/50 transition duration-300">
                <summary class="font-bold text-white cursor-pointer text-base md:text-lg flex justify-between items-center list-none select-none">
                    <span>What is "Raising" an idea?</span>
                    <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line text-slate-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300 text-xl"></i>
                </summary>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mt-4 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-800 pt-4 text-sm md:text-base">
                    "Raising" is similar to an upvote or a "like" on other platforms. However, on Ideate, it signifies moreâ€”it means you see potential in the concept and want to see it built. Ideas with the most Raises appear on the "Hall of Fame".
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-slate-900 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 group open:border-blue-500/50 transition duration-300">
                <summary class="font-bold text-white cursor-pointer text-base md:text-lg flex justify-between items-center list-none select-none">
                    <span>Is my intellectual property safe here?</span>
                    <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line text-slate-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300 text-xl"></i>
                </summary>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mt-4 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-800 pt-4 text-sm md:text-base">
                    Ideate is an open platform. While our community guidelines prohibit theft, <strong>we recommend not posting sensitive trade secrets or patent-pending mechanics</strong>. Share the "What" and "Why", but keep the proprietary "How" to yourself until you are protected.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-slate-900 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 group open:border-blue-500/50 transition duration-300">
                <summary class="font-bold text-white cursor-pointer text-base md:text-lg flex justify-between items-center list-none select-none">
                    <span>Can I collaborate with other users?</span>
                    <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line text-slate-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300 text-xl"></i>
                </summary>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mt-4 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-800 pt-4 text-sm md:text-base">
                    Absolutely! That's the whole point. You can use the comments section to offer help. In the future, we are launching a "Join Team" feature to formalize partnerships.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-slate-900 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 group open:border-blue-500/50 transition duration-300">
                <summary class="font-bold text-white cursor-pointer text-base md:text-lg flex justify-between items-center list-none select-none">
                    <span>How do I change my Profile Picture?</span>
                    <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line text-slate-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300 text-xl"></i>
                </summary>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mt-4 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-800 pt-4 text-sm md:text-base">
                    Go to <a href="/settings" class="text-blue-400 underline hover:text-blue-300">Settings</a> via the sidebar or clicking your profile. Click on your current avatar to upload a new image. We support JPG and PNG formats up to 5MB.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-slate-900 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 group open:border-blue-500/50 transition duration-300">
                <summary class="font-bold text-white cursor-pointer text-base md:text-lg flex justify-between items-center list-none select-none">
                    <span>Can I delete my account?</span>
                    <i class="ri-arrow-down-s-line text-slate-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300 text-xl"></i>
                </summary>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mt-4 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-800 pt-4 text-sm md:text-base">
                    Yes. In the Settings page, scroll to the bottom "Danger Zone". Deleting your account is permanent and will remove all your posted ideas and comments.
                </p>
            </details>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script>
        window.toggleSidebar = function() {
            const sidebar = document.getElementById('mobileSidebar');
            if (sidebar) {
                if (sidebar.classList.contains('-translate-x-full')) {
                    sidebar.classList.remove('-translate-x-full');
                } else {
                    sidebar.classList.add('-translate-x-full');
                }
            }
        };

        document.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            const sidebar = document.getElementById('mobileSidebar');
            const menuBtn = e.target.closest('button[onclick="window.toggleSidebar()"]');
            
            if (window.innerWidth < 768 && sidebar && !sidebar.contains(e.target) && !menuBtn && !sidebar.classList.contains('-translate-x-full')) {
                sidebar.classList.add('-translate-x-full');
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>